| Role                    | Can View All Repo Alerts | Can Manage GHAS Settings | Receives Notifications |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------ | ------------------------ | ---------------------- |
| **Org Owner**           | âœ… Yes                    | âœ… Yes                    | âœ… For security events  |
| **Security Manager**    | âœ… Yes (all repos)        | âŒ Limited                | âœ… Yes                  |
| **Repo Admins**         | âœ… Yes (their repos)      | âœ… Yes (repo-level only)  | âœ… Yes                  |
| **Write Collaborators** | âœ… Yes (their repos)      | âŒ No                     | âŒ Not by default       |

> ğŸ” **Security Managers** are a special role you can assign to users/groups to view **security alerts across all repos** even if theyâ€™re not collaborators.

